      <title>进入新特朗普时代，新兴市场高风险债券继续吸引交易员</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-10/going-into-new-trump-era-risky-emerging-market-bonds-keep-luring-traders</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普当选后，发展中国家的垃圾级美元债券正吸引瑞银资产管理公司、拉扎德资产管理有限公司和 PGIM 固定收益基金经理的新一轮押注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-10/going-into-new-trump-era-risky-emerging-market-bonds-keep-luring-traders</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 10 Nov 2024 13:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新兴市场动态：交易员应对特朗普 2.0（播客）</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/audio/2024-11-10/what-s-happening-in-em-traders-grapple-with-trump-2-0-podcast</link>
      <description><![CDATA[维尼修斯安德拉德 (Vinicius Andrade) 与宋子嘉 (Zijia Song) 在纽约讨论唐纳德特朗普第二任总统对新兴市场资产的潜在影响，以及投资者为何青睐高收益主权债务和公司债券而非投资级债券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/audio/2024-11-10/what-s-happening-in-em-traders-grapple-with-trump-2-0-podcast</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 10 Nov 2024 13:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
